From 394cdf3bfd1788624ba76dc880b2ab01d2a666fc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alejandro Pena <adpena@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 2026 23:13:51 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] codex-core: retire finalized spawned agents and drain live
 descendants on root shutdown
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Complements PR #19753 by closing two structural gaps it doesn't address:
finalized (`Completed` / `Errored`) spawned agents now retire from live slot
ownership while preserving cached final status, and root-session shutdown
drains live spawned descendants before tearing down conversation / MCP / etc.

Defect 1 — registry-level retirement:
- `AgentMetadata` gains `last_status: Option<AgentStatus>` and `slot_active`.
- `AgentRegistry::retire_spawned_thread(thread_id, status)` caches the final
  status, flips `slot_active = false`, and decrements `total_count` once.
- `AgentControl::retire_finalized_agent(thread_id, status)` is invoked by the
  completion watcher when status transitions to `Completed` / `Errored`.
  `Shutdown` is intentionally not retired (regressed an existing resume-path
  test).
- `get_status` / `wait_agent` / `list_agents` fall back to cached registry
  status when no live thread exists. `resume_agent` switches to
  `has_live_thread(thread_id)` instead of treating any non-`NotFound` as
  proof of non-resumability.

Defect 2 — live-descendant drain on root shutdown:
- `session::handlers::shutdown` now calls
  `live_thread_spawn_descendants(root_thread_id)` and submits shutdown to
  each, before and after `conversation.shutdown()`.
- The spawned-agent registry is cleared at the end only when no live
  descendants remain detectable.

Hygiene:
- `SpawnReservation::Drop` releases the reserved nickname when spawn setup
  fails before commit.

Verification on this branch:
- `cargo fmt --all -- --check` ok.
- `cargo clippy -p codex-core --tests -- -D warnings` clean.
- `cargo test -p codex-core --lib retire_releases_slot_and_preserves_cached_status` ok.
- `cargo test -p codex-core --lib spawn_agent_releases_slot_after_completion` ok.
- `cargo test -p codex-core --lib root_shutdown_shuts_down_live_spawned_descendants` ok.
- `cargo test -p codex-core --lib failed_spawn_releases_reserved_nickname` ok.
